  <thing id="wSGEstoc" name="Estoc" description="An estoc is a piercing sword with no edge and a triangular, square, or hexagonal cross-section of its “blade” that give it greater durability and thrusting power but no ability to make slashing or cutting attacks (though it can also be used to deliver powerful crushing blows). The estoc can be used as a one-handed martial weapon when mounted, and as a two-handed martial weapon when on foot.  \n\nAn estoc is considered to be part of heavy blades weapon group for purposes of the weapon training fighter class feature." compset="Weapon">
