  <thing id="wSGCinqued" name="Cinquedea" description=" Considered either a long dagger and very short sword (depending on the culture), the cinquedea has a heavy, thick blade roughly 15 inches\nlong with multiple grooves running its length. The blade is very wide at the base (the weapon’s name means “five fingers,” and refers to the blade’s width at its base) and tapers to a sharp point. \n\nA cinquedea is considered to be part of light blades weapon group for purposes of the weapon training fighter class feature." compset="Weapon">
